WARNINGS:
1) Do not enable TSO for SDRAM/DDR1 diveces (BUGGY!!!)

RECOMENDATIONS:
1) If cpu have L2 cache try disable optimize inlining (allow force inline) and enable GRO - may be fastest

BUILD:
1) cd toolchain and start build_toolchain.sh as root
2) cd in projectroot (/opt/Wive-MT) and start compile <target name> or compile-releases for build all targets

#############################################################################################################
CURRENT HOOKS FOR ADVANCED USER LOGIC:

1) /etc/udhcp.d - scripts start after udcp renew event
2) /etc/ip(6)tables.d - scripts start after netfilter configure
3) /etc/ppp-l2tpsrv/ip-up(down).d - scripts start after client connect(disconnect) to VPN server
4) /etc/ppp/ip-up(down).d - scripts start after router connetc(disconnect) to external VPN server
5) /etc/scripts/wan_up.sh - this script start after WAN up and full services reinit
#############################################################################################################
